sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant O as Orchestrator<br/>(session context)
    participant SDK as gsd-sdk / gsd-tools
    participant FS as .planning/
    participant A as Agents<br/>(fresh 200K each)
    participant GIT as Git

    Note over U,GIT: PROJECT INIT (once)
    U->>O: /gsd-new-project
    O->>SDK: init new-project
    SDK-->>O: domain context
    O->>A: spawn 4 researchers (parallel)
    A-->>FS: domain research
    O->>A: spawn research-synthesizer
    A-->>FS: SUMMARY.md
    O->>A: spawn roadmapper
    A-->>FS: ROADMAP.md + REQUIREMENTS.md + PROJECT.md

    Note over U,GIT: PHASE DISCUSS
    U->>O: /gsd-discuss-phase 1
    O->>SDK: init phase-op 1
    SDK-->>O: phase context
    O->>U: implementation questions
    U->>O: answers (gray areas resolved)
    O->>FS: write CONTEXT.md (locked decisions)

    Note over U,GIT: PLAN PHASE
    U->>O: /gsd-plan-phase 1
    O->>SDK: init plan-phase 1
    O->>A: spawn researcher + pattern-mapper (parallel)
    A-->>FS: RESEARCH.md + PATTERNS.md
    O->>A: spawn planner
    A-->>FS: plan-1.md, plan-2.md, plan-3.md
    O->>A: spawn plan-checker
    A-->>O: checker verdict
    alt Revision needed
        O->>A: spawn planner (revision mode)
        A-->>FS: updated plans
        O->>A: spawn plan-checker again
    end

    Note over U,GIT: EXECUTE PHASE
    U->>O: /gsd-execute-phase 1
    O->>SDK: init execute-phase 1
    SDK-->>O: PLAN.md files + wave grouping
    Note over O,A: Wave 1 — parallel
    O->>A: spawn executor (plan-1) [fresh ctx]
    O->>A: spawn executor (plan-2) [fresh ctx]
    A->>GIT: implement task 1 → commit
    A->>GIT: implement task 2 → commit
    A->>GIT: implement task 3 → commit
    A-->>FS: write SUMMARY.md
    Note over O,A: Wait for all Wave 1
    Note over O,A: Wave 2 — parallel
    O->>A: spawn executor (plan-3) [fresh ctx]
    A->>GIT: implement + commit

    Note over U,GIT: VERIFY WORK
    U->>O: /gsd-verify-work 1
    O->>SDK: init verify-work 1
    O->>A: spawn verifier [fresh ctx]
    A->>FS: read plans + summaries + codebase
    A-->>FS: write VERIFICATION.md
    alt Gaps found
        O->>U: present fix plans
        U->>O: approve
        O->>A: spawn executors for fixes
    end

    Note over U,GIT: SHIP
    U->>O: /gsd-ship 1
    O->>A: spawn code-reviewer [fresh ctx]
    A-->>O: REVIEW.md findings
    O->>GIT: gh pr create (auto-body from artifacts)
    O->>U: PR URL
